AB  - Natural language processing and machine learning technologies have acquired considerable importance, especially in disciplines where the main information is contained in free text documents rather than in relational databases. TEXTCROWD is an advanced cloud based tool developed within the framework of EOSCpilot project for processing textual archaeological reports. The tool has been boosted and made capable of browsing big online knowledge repositories, educating itself on demand and used for producing semantic metadata ready to be integrated with information coming from different domains, to establish an advanced machine learning scenario.
