TI  - 3D Model Acquisition and Image Processing for the Virtual Musealization of the Spezieria di Santa Maria della Scala, Rome
AU  - Pascual, MLVD
AU  - Fantoni, R
AU  - Francucci, M
AU  - Guarneri, M
AU  - Mongelli, M
AU  - Pierattini, S
